cu.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to 'invalid' will cause configuration rejection as gNB ID must be in hexadecimal format.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to 'invalid' will cause configuration rejection as gNB ID must be in hexadecimal format.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_ID 設定為 'invalid' 會導致配置拒絕，因為 gNB ID 必須是十六進制格式。
